headline: Is It Too Late To Consider C.H. Robinson Worldwide (CHRW) After Strong Multi Year Share Gains?
summary: If you are wondering whether C.H. Robinson Worldwide's current share price still offers value, this article walks through what the numbers actually say about the stock. The share price sits at US$185.25 after a 2.5% decline over the last week and a 4.4% decline over the last month.
